d that payday loans are, by definition, desperate remedies, if you are still in need of a payday loan, our research indicates three companies that are worthy of your attention: <a href=\"/payday-loan-service-reviewuk/quick-quid-review/\">QuickQuid</a>, <a href=\"/payday-loan-service-reviewuk/payday-bank-review/\">Payday Bank</a> and <a href=\"/payday-loan-service-reviewuk/kwik-cash-review/\">Kwik Cash</a>.","Remember that the lender has extended money to you on the premise that you have a job and will repay the loan when your next paycheck arrives. If you fail to repay the loan within a month, you run the risk of falling into indentured financial servitude. Therefore, payday loans should be considered instruments of last resort.","By the time you take out one of these cash loans, all of the normal emergency defenses must have been breached. You did not put away emergency funds. You failed to qualify for a credit card, or your cards are at their credit limits. You have either tapped out all of your family and friends for loans or you just don t want them to know about your situation. At this point, all the sermons in the world will not help when you need a payday loan to fix your broken-down car. Unless you pay  200 immediately, you are going to miss days of work because of lack of transportation.","A payday lender could have the money in your account within 15 minutes. On your next payday, you repay the loan along with a  50 charge, and all is well because you have made appropriate use of the service and limited your exposure to astronomical interest rates. Now your thoughts are not focused on how usurious or predatory the lender was, but on how a payday loan smoothed out your income so that you could absorb and recover from an emergency car repair that didn t prevent you from going to work.","At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don t Have To. "]},"id":"68cf96d1-988a-40e0-9d1f-a5bbbdc335df","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_7293","url":"/p